-- Simbhaoli Sugars Says Considering Options for Setting Up Kandla Refinery
-- Pradeep Kurup
-- 2010-06-17T07:32:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/simbhaoli-sugars-says-considering-options-for-setting-up-kandla-refinery.html

          
          
             Simbhaoli Sugars Ltd. is considering
“various options” for setting up a refinery with 1,000 metric
tons per day capacity in Kandla at an estimated cost of 20
billion rupees, the company said in a statement to the Bombay
Stock Exchange today. Simbhaoli is considering a venture to
procure raw sugar and export white sugar, the statement said.  
          
          


  


        